data.description: Garden District Charm at its finest !! Relax on the spacious front porch or entertain family and friends on the large deck and enclosed back porch that overlooks a well maintained back yard. This home features 3 spacious bed rooms and two full baths and new appliances in an accommodating kitchen. Prepared meals can be served in the adjacent dining room that features built in cabinets or move to the enclosed back porch for a more casual setting. The living room is large with high ceilings and a working fireplace/. This home has great flow , large windows, high ceilings and beautiful hardwood floors in every room
